---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="JAAMD Example">
    <h1>JAAMD Example</h1>
    <p>
      This is a local development playground for the <strong>jaamd</strong>
      integration. It is <em>not built or published</em> as part of the package
      — it lives only in the repository to make it easy to test changes locally.
    </p>
    <p>
      Head to <a href="/demo">Demo</a> to see all features in action, or
      run <code>pnpm dev</code> inside this <code>example/</code> folder
      and open <code>http://localhost:4321</code> in your browser.
    </p>
    <h2>Quick Start</h2>
    <pre><code class="language-sh">cd example
pnpm install
pnpm dev</code></pre>
</Layout>
